"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:10.5.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">10.5.2</span> 标题：手镯、臂镯、脚镯（bracelet, armlet, anklet）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֶצְעָדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’ets‘adah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֶכֶס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘ekes)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:18\">ISA 3:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צָמִיד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsamid)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:30\">GEN 24:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:47\">GEN 24:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:11\">EZK 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:42\">EZK 23:42</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צְעָדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ts‘adah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:20\">ISA 3:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：χλιδών</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chlidōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir21:21\">SIR 21:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ψέλιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：pselion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0532_bracelets_gold.jpg\" alt=\"以羚羊头装饰的手镯\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">以羚羊头装饰的手镯 (Walters Art Museum, Public domain, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>手镯／臂镯是戴在手腕／手臂上的一种首饰，为圆形，用金属做成。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>手镯戴在手腕上，而臂镯通常佩戴在肘部以上。如果必须要区分手臂的各个部分，希伯来文<em>tsamid</em> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:11\">EZK 16:11</a> 中可以翻译为“手腕上的镯子”。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a> ：如果没有不同的词来区分戴在手腕上的环和戴在上臂的环，那么在这节经文中，可以使用一个集合名词，例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 译为“珠宝”（“jewelry”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>翻译者必须注意，不要使用表示戴在手臂上面但不是用金属做成物件的词语。例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:10\">2SA 1:10</a> 中译为“arm-band”（“臂带”），但在现代英文中，人们可能会误以为这是布料或塑料做成的袖章。</p>\n<p>关于希伯来文<em>‘ekes</em> 和<em>ts‘adah</em> ，参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">10.5 珠宝、首饰、饰物 (jewelry, ornaments)&lt;REALIA:10.5&gt;</a> 就<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:18-Isa3:23\">ISA 3:18–ISA 3:23</a> 所做的讨论。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:4\">JDT 10:4</a> 中，希腊文<em>chlidōn</em> 和<em>pselion</em> 都可以既指（戴在手臂上的）“手镯”，又指（戴在脚上的）“脚镯”。如果目标语言有分别表示“手镯”和“脚镯”的词语，那么本节经文可以同时使用这两个词；或者也可以说，“戴在手腕和脚踝上的金属饰带。”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
